{
  "texts": [
    "Evaluating the models' responses involved human verification and metrics like chrF and METEOR for queries related to both textual and visual elements from the uploaded PDF guideline.",
    "Throughout the evaluation process, questions were put into the MedDoc-Bot interface, prompting each model to generate responses.",
    "Posing the same questions to all tested models allowed us to compare consistency, fidelity, and relevance of answers between models.",
    "Additionally, we recorded the time taken by each model to generate responses to each query.We conducted a comprehensive dual assessment, evaluating the human relevance of the generated responses.",
    "This involved assessing their meaningfulness and accuracy in addressing medical queries and their fidelity to the original guideline text."
  ]
}